
---

## `.gitignore`

For a Cocotb + Verilator/Icarus project:

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.pytest_cache/

# Cocotb
results.xml

# Waveforms
*.vcd
*.fst
*.wlf

# Verilator
obj_dir/
*.o
*.d

# Simulation
sim_build/
*.log

# VS Code
.vscode/

# JetBrains
.idea/

# Linux
*~

# macOS
.DS_Store
